---
source: tests/degraded_honesty.rs
assertion: daemon foreground mode runs bounded supervised maintenance handlers
schema:
  foreground: ee.steward.daemon_foreground.v1
  status: ee.steward.daemon_status.v1
contracts:
  - daemon foreground requires explicit bounded execution
